{"tid":1219754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美孚嘅朋友仔 加油！","createTime":"2019-06-14T00:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T03:02:35.000Z","uid":71274,"like":78,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5b3904977bd858926c7b72da51bfbca804ea091f","tid":1219754,"uid":71274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PPedJrL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPPedJrL.png&h=7fa11510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"697deff25677342b28c83d9c9c72aedc3c3c5644","tid":1219754,"uid":133412,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:55:18.000Z","msg":"唔應該係你哋跪呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa77d9cbe3b6c20691e887f6140c209e7fffecb","tid":1219754,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e82fefa151d236768e25a2c57bc6b2371245b46","tid":1219754,"uid":73293,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:57:17.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不要小看網絡平台的威力，<br />\n每多一個發聲，<br />\n就多一份力量！！！</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家可以都叫朋友係自己既網絡平台到發聲<br />\n呢個係其中一個發聲方法<br />\n不要俾政府睇死<br />\n我地係唔會就咁屈服強權</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一齊呼籲香港KOL清晰表明立場去發聲！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">急！！需要大家幫手！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1219585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1219585</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n你好，<br />\n作為香港既KOL, 係應該做Key Opinion Leader應該做既事！<br />\n如果你是支持這次香港的抗爭運動，希望你能夠發揮不同角色的作用，係你既網絡平台上發聲！<br />\n<br />\n作歌既可以作歌，拍片既可以拍片，寫文既可以寫文。<br />\n但絕對唔係求其出個story, 影下地下，影下天空，就話自己緊張香港。<br />\n<br />\n亦希望你清楚表明自己的立場，不是食大茶飯講d唔講d, 而係真真正正講出你對引渡法既睇法！<br />\n<br />\n當你口說支持，但又沒有就著KOL的角色，在網絡平台沒有就香港的抗爭作出清晰的回應和表明立場，身為Key Opinion Leader, 你慚愧嗎？"},{"pid":"415a3e800b810f2945c617da3934b052ebe076fc","tid":1219754,"uid":13594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ce9daafb6b47a1ccbd07d3db703d3230e1744f","tid":1219754,"uid":248089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:00:01.000Z","msg":"岩先都見到，然後後面個廢老係度嘈「點解咁多人死唔見你地死」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家行過可以同佢地講聲加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f89c16f803e5e3549e9509657a95902f471ec3d8","tid":1219754,"uid":21279,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"10ce9daafb6b47a1ccbd07d3db703d3230e1744f","tid":1219754,"uid":248089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:00:01.000Z","msg":"岩先都見到，然後後面個廢老係度嘈「點解咁多人死唔見你地死」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家行過可以同